      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Ts'aou ch'ung.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>陟彼南山，言采其薇，未見君子，我心傷悲，亦既見止，亦既覯止，我心則夷。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I ascended that hill in the south,
And gathered the thorn-ferns.
While I do not see my lord,
My sorrowful heart is wounded with grief.
Let me have seen him,
Let me have met him,
And my heart will then be at peace.</seg>
      </tuv>
